## ğŸ¯ Project Overview

This project is a machine learning-based sentiment analysis system for Chinese social media, focusing on sentiment classification (positive/negative) of Weibo posts. The system implements a complete machine learning workflow and trains/evaluates multiple machine learning models on 119,988 labeled Weibo posts.

### Core Features
- ğŸ” **Real-time Sentiment Analysis**: Input Chinese text and get instant sentiment predictions with confidence scores
- ğŸ“Š **Model Performance Comparison**: Visual comparison of different models' accuracy, F1 scores, and other metrics
- ğŸ› ï¸ **Complete Processing Pipeline**: Shows the full text processing flow including cleaning, segmentation, and feature extraction
- ğŸŒ **Cloud Deployment**: Online access without local environment configuration
- ğŸ”„ **Multi-language Interface**: Full bilingual support (Chinese/English)

